&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an energetic, polished individual with exceptional communication skills and a talent for relationship building.&amp;nbsp; The successful candidate will gain expertise in accurately capturing and qualifying leads, effectively managing a sales pipeline, and achieving quarterly revenue targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This Business Development Representative provides a challenging career opportunity as well as career advancement within D2L.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How will I make an impact?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for exceeding objectives within your assigned territory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to understand and deliver D2L&#39;s unique value proposition and create solution vision with prospects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively participate in outbound calling campaigns to generate sales opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accurately capture and qualify leads gathered from tradeshows, webinars, inbound calls, and other marketing initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow-up with existing D2L contacts and develop them into sales prospects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Distribute leads and make qualified appointments for Sales Executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and respond to D2L Sales inbox and website inquiries – responding and re-directing incoming customer request for information, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and update lead generation emails and phone scripts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update customer interactions through the CRM tool&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

